{"tid":1091272,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【望自立門戶】有望抱豬B？ 何猷啟承認造人計劃進行中","createTime":"2019-04-04T04:32:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T08:16:29.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a53bd32ba2c72fa17887033dce135b92920a58d5","tid":1091272,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T04:32:05.000Z","msg":"賭王何鴻燊兒子何猷啟與王賢誌（Vinci），今日出席東華三院就職禮，Vinci正式卸任，並由蔡榮星榮升主席。<br />\n猷啟第4年擔任東華總理，他指做慈善能幫到人特別高興，問到今年的工作大計，猷啟希望事業更上一層樓：「希望可以有自己嘅小生意，一直幫緊屋企，希望可以自己搞，而家計劃緊，都有問阿媽同家姐意見。」問到會否趕快完成做爸爸這項人生計劃時，猷啟說：「做爸爸計劃緊。」但他就不肯透露今年有沒有機會成為爸爸。<br />\n猷啟隨後又表示太太GiGi因身體抱恙，故今晚不會出席晚宴，問到是否懷孕不適時，猷啟就話：「唔係，我媽咪感冒唔舒服，佢要照顧媽媽。」提到三太會否催要抱孫？他則說：「唔會，佢好民主。」而家姐超盈懷孕，猷啟表示已恭喜對方，並謂有喜事十分開心。<br />\n提到何超蓮最近拍了飲品廣告，會否覺得家姐想當明星？猷啟說：「又唔同路線，佢有自己計劃，開心就得。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190403/large/1554283611_366e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190403%2Flarge%2F1554283611_366e.jpg&h=e53698dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190403/59445641\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190403%2F59445641&d=xTo9lt5%2FMO3GrXFnFHQdvC3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=07fbfeaf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190403%2F59445641&h=4b35b75c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190403/59445641</a>"},{"pid":"eb78c11b486a182a49a0a08129d018cd11f4c33d","tid":1091272,"uid":152123,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T04:33:50.000Z","msg":"本post頭三話題：<br />\n刷首抽<br />\n想幫佢含撚<br />\n窮人唔好生仔"},{"pid":"c4ba9167b32326fef63a48e7b9d9bb3bad90daee","tid":1091272,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb78c11b486a182a49a0a08129d018cd11f4c33d","tid":1091272,"uid":152123,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T04:33:50.000Z","msg":"本post頭三話題：<br />\n刷首抽<br />\n想幫佢含撚<br />\n窮人唔好生仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T08:16:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}